---
import EventLayout from '../../layouts/EventLayout.astro';
import SectionDivider from '../../components/SectionDivider.astro';
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<EventLayout
  title="Bringing Back Sunday — Renewing Culture Conference"
  description="The 2nd Annual Renewing Culture Conference gathers Christians from across Western Canada for two days of talks, seminars, prayer, and fellowship. October 2–3, 2026 at Mount Carmel Spirituality Centre, Alberta."
  ogImage="/images/og/conference-2026-og.jpg"
  date="2026-10-02"
  endDate="2026-10-03"
  location="Mount Carmel Spirituality Centre, Parkland County"
  locationAddress="Mount Carmel Spirituality Centre, 1225 Township Rd 535, Parkland County, AB T7Y 0H5"
  showMap={true}
  image="/images/events/2026-renewing-culture-conference-art.jpg"
  artFilter={true}
  imageAlt="Adoration of the Mystic Lamb — van Eyck"
  tag="Annual Flagship Conference"
  ctaText="Registration Starting Soon"
  ctaHref="#register"
  ctaStatus="closed"
>
  <p>
    The 2nd Annual <strong>Renewing Culture Conference</strong> gathers Christians from across Western Canada
    for two days of talks, seminars, prayer, and fellowship. This year's theme —
    <em>Bringing Back Sunday</em> — takes up Josef Pieper's masterwork
    <em>Leisure: The Basis of Culture</em>.
  </p>

  <p>
    In a world that reduces human life to productivity and consumption, Pieper's vision of
    contemplative leisure as the foundation of civilization is more urgent than ever. What would
    it mean to recover the Lord's Day — not just as a day off, but as the source of authentic culture?
  </p>

  <h2>What to Expect</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Keynote addresses from leading Catholic thinkers</li>
    <li>Breakout seminars and Socratic discussion groups</li>
    <li>Daily Mass and prayer</li>
    <li>Meals and fellowship with like-minded Christians</li>
    <li>Book signings and a curated reading table</li>
  </ul>

  <p>
    All are welcome — no prerequisites.
  </p>

  <SectionDivider />

  <!-- Registration (coming soon) -->
  <div id="register" class="conference-register">
    <div class="register-header">
      <p class="label text-gold">Registration</p>
      <h2>Registration Starting Soon</h2>
      <p class="register-subtitle">Tickets include all sessions, meals, and materials.</p>
      <button class="register-btn--disabled" disabled>Registration Starting Soon</button>
      <p class="register-coming-soon">Check back shortly — registration opens soon.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</EventLayout>

<style>
  .conference-register {
    margin-top: 48px;
    padding-top: 16px;
  }

  .register-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .register-header h2 {
    margin-top: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .register-subtitle {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--color-gray);
  }

  .register-btn--disabled {
    font-family: var(--font-display, Georgia, serif);
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 14px 32px;
    background-color: var(--color-gray, #999);
    color: #fff;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 3px;
    cursor: not-allowed;
    opacity: 0.6;
    margin-top: 20px;
  }

  .register-coming-soon {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--color-gray);
    font-style: italic;
    margin-top: 12px;
  }
</style>
